{"type": "article", "id": 14051, "title": "存放信件的笔记本", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-27T07:48:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000305Zy2NQpOVf1qHWUcJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦家居品牌 Hay 推出了一个外形像本子的“口袋”，可以存放各类各样的名片、信件。因为是纸做的，打开时就像打开一把纸折的扇子，而渐变的颜色也模拟了花朵绽放的样子。这个系列拥有 A3、A4 不同规格和多种颜色，A4 型号 29 欧元、A3 型 36 欧元。<a href=\"http://www.connox.com/categories/papeterie/notebooks/hay-plisse.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141654vbrtRWC2Gh5iO0a3.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141655hJkSrt7zx4aGRgPK.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141655Yo2w0UtcNxDnFVM4.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}